comments: Nwora (MIL) brushes Rozier's (CHA) left arm and marginal contact occurs as Rozier drives inside the perimeter.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Middleton (MIL) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly awarded to Charlotte.

Antetokounmpo (MIL) extends for the rebound and marginal contact occurs with Bridges' (CHA) right arm and side as he back-taps the ball.

Portis (MIL) engages and disengages with Bridges (CHA) as Bridges moves to set the pick.
Ball (CHA) brings his off-arm toward Middleton's (MIL) right side when marginal contact occurs as Ball slows his momentum and releases away.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he could be deemed to be imminently actively guarding an opponent.

Ball (CHA) makes contact with the ball and the part of Antetokounmpo's (MIL) hand that is on the ball after his gather. Washington (CHA) turns alongside Antetokounmpo's path and absorbs the marginal body contact before making further contact with the ball.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: The ball touches Washington's (CHA) right thigh last before going out of bounds.  Possession should have been awarded to Milwaukee.
Bridges (CHA) brings his hands toward Middleton's (MIL) side as he sets the pick and releases away from Middleton when he turns to roll.
Bridges (CHA) establishes himself in bounds prior to receiving the pass.

Portis (MIL) establishes himself in a screening position in Washington's (CHA) path and does not deliver the contact as the switch takes place.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) gathers the ball on his left foot and takes two steps before elevating for the shot.

Replay review of the foul called on Bridges (CHA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Bridges extends forward and initiates body contact with Antetokounmpo (MIL) during the driving shot attempt.
Portis (MIL) and Washington (CHA) engage and disengage with one another after the free throw attempt is released.

Matthews (MIL) and Bridges (CHA) engage and disengage with one another during rebounding.

Washington (CHA) moves toward Middleton (MIL) after Middleton picks up his dribble and marginal body contact occurs.
Washington (CHA) and Connaughton (MIL) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Washington (CHA) retreats in a vertical position alongside Antetokounmpo's (MIL) path and absorbs the body contact that occurs after Antetokounmpo passes the ball.
